entry.title: EtheaDev/SVGIconImageList
entry.summary: Four advanced components to simplify use of SVG images and SVG icons into ImageList: TSVGIconImage, TSVGIconImageCollection, TSVGIconVirtualImageList, TSVGIconImageList (for VCL and FMX). Choose the preferred engine to render SVG (Delphi Image32, SKIA4Delphi, Direct2D);
